        In this example, you can see how to render and configure points in a particular range by using <a target="_blank" href="https://ej2.syncfusion.com/aspnetcore/documentation/chart/chart-types/area#multicolored-area" aria-label="Navigate to the documentation for multicolored-area in ASP.NET Core Chart component">MultiColoredArea</a> series. Points within the range can be configured with the <a target="_blank" href="https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/aspnetcore-js2/Syncfusion.EJ2.Charts.ChartSegment.html#Syncfusion_EJ2_Charts_ChartSegment_Color" aria-label="Navigate to the color property reference for ASP.NET Core Chart Segment">Color</a> property in <code>ChartSegment</code>.
